channel.description: Recent content on Big Data in Biomedicine

item.description: I am studying Bioinformatics at the TUM and LMU as my master since 2019. I am joining the ListLab as a HIWI to continue the project of my group from the SystemsBiomedicine practical course, where we introduced a new shiny-application to explore the microbiome, including co-occurrence analysis and clustering by functional topics.
